{
  "video_id": "CY_Oj59WlL0",
  "title": "Susan Solomon: The promise of research with stem cells",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16381.0,
      "end_time": 19370.0,
      "text": "So, embryonic stem cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19370.0,
      "end_time": 22670.0,
      "text": "are really incredible cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22670.0,
      "end_time": 25458.0,
      "text": "They are our body&#39;s own repair kits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25458.0,
      "end_time": 28421.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re pluripotent, which means they can morph into"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28422.0,
      "end_time": 30854.0,
      "text": "all of the cells in our bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30854.0,
      "end_time": 33542.0,
      "text": "Soon, we actually will be able to use stem cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33542.0,
      "end_time": 36527.0,
      "text": "to replace cells that are damaged or diseased."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36527.0,
      "end_time": 38958.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not what I want to talk to you about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38958.0,
      "end_time": 41635.0,
      "text": "because right now there are some really"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41636.0,
      "end_time": 45582.0,
      "text": "extraordinary things that we are doing with stem cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45582.0,
      "end_time": 47189.0,
      "text": "that are completely changing"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47189.0,
      "end_time": 50880.0,
      "text": "the way we look and model disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50880.0,
      "end_time": 52607.0,
      "text": "our ability to understand why we get sick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52607.0,
      "end_time": 55380.0,
      "text": "and even develop drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55380.0,
      "end_time": 59351.0,
      "text": "I truly believe that stem cell research is going to allow"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59351.0,
      "end_time": 63856.0,
      "text": "our children to look at Alzheimer&#39;s and diabetes"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63856.0,
      "end_time": 68247.0,
      "text": "and other major diseases the way we view polio today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68247.0,
      "end_time": 71448.0,
      "text": "which is as a preventable disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71448.0,
      "end_time": 74670.0,
      "text": "So here we have this incredible field, which has"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74671.0,
      "end_time": 79580.0,
      "text": "enormous hope for humanity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79580.0,
      "end_time": 82578.0,
      "text": "but much like IVF over 35 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82578.0,
      "end_time": 84912.0,
      "text": "until the birth of a healthy baby, Louise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84912.0,
      "end_time": 89981.0,
      "text": "this field has been under siege politically and financially."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89981.0,
      "end_time": 94253.0,
      "text": "Critical research is being challenged instead of supported,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94253.0,
      "end_time": 98613.0,
      "text": "and we saw that it was really essential to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98613.0,
      "end_time": 102144.0,
      "text": "private safe haven laboratories where this work"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102144.0,
      "end_time": 104974.0,
      "text": "could be advanced without interference."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104974.0,
      "end_time": 107505.0,
      "text": "And so, in 2005,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107505.0,
      "end_time": 110116.0,
      "text": "we started the New York Stem Cell Foundation Laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110117.0,
      "end_time": 113706.0,
      "text": "so that we would have a small organization that could"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113706.0,
      "end_time": 117180.0,
      "text": "do this work and support it."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117180.0,
      "end_time": 120403.0,
      "text": "What we saw very quickly is the world of both medical"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120403.0,
      "end_time": 123779.0,
      "text": "research, but also developing drugs and treatments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123779.0,
      "end_time": 127491.0,
      "text": "is dominated by, as you would expect, large organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127492.0,
      "end_time": 130611.0,
      "text": "but in a new field, sometimes large organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130610.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132779.0,
      "text": "really have trouble getting out of their own way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132779.0,
      "end_time": 135215.0,
      "text": "and sometimes they can&#39;t ask the right questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135215.0,
      "end_time": 138571.0,
      "text": "and there is an enormous gap that&#39;s just gotten larger"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 138571.0,
      "end_time": 141782.0,
      "text": "between academic research on the one hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 141782.0,
      "end_time": 144483.0,
      "text": "and pharmaceutical companies and biotechs"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 144483.0,
      "end_time": 147749.0,
      "text": "that are responsible for delivering all of our drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 147749.0,
      "end_time": 150138.0,
      "text": "and many of our treatments, and so we knew that"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 150139.0,
      "end_time": 154850.0,
      "text": "to really accelerate cures and therapies, we were going"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154850.0,
      "end_time": 156892.0,
      "text": "to have to address this with two things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156892.0,
      "end_time": 160114.0,
      "text": "new technologies and also a new research model."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160114.0,
      "end_time": 163873.0,
      "text": "Because if you don&#39;t close that gap, you really are"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163873.0,
      "end_time": 165480.0,
      "text": "exactly where we are today."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165480.0,
      "end_time": 167147.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what I want to focus on."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 167147.0,
      "end_time": 170697.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve spent the last couple of years pondering this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170697.0,
      "end_time": 173880.0,
      "text": "making a list of the different things that we had to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 173880.0,
      "end_time": 175719.0,
      "text": "and so we developed a new technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 175719.0,
      "end_time": 176970.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s software and hardware,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176970.0,
      "end_time": 180473.0,
      "text": "that actually can generate thousands and thousands of"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180473.0,
      "end_time": 183643.0,
      "text": "genetically diverse stem cell lines to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183643.0,
      "end_time": 187430.0,
      "text": "a global array, essentially avatars of ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187430.0,
      "end_time": 190864.0,
      "text": "And we did this because we think that it&#39;s actually going"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190864.0,
      "end_time": 194279.0,
      "text": "to allow us to realize the potential, the promise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 194279.0,
      "end_time": 197359.0,
      "text": "of all of the sequencing of the human genome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197359.0,
      "end_time": 199863.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s going to allow us, in doing that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199863.0,
      "end_time": 204871.0,
      "text": "to actually do clinical trials in a dish with human cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204871.0,
      "end_time": 209300.0,
      "text": "not animal cells, to generate drugs and treatments"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 209300.0,
      "end_time": 212279.0,
      "text": "that are much more effective, much safer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 212279.0,
      "end_time": 215535.0,
      "text": "much faster, and at a much lower cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 215535.0,
      "end_time": 217918.0,
      "text": "So let me put that in perspective for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 217919.0,
      "end_time": 219335.0,
      "text": "and give you some context."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219335.0,
      "end_time": 224167.0,
      "text": "This is an extremely new field."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 224167.0,
      "end_time": 226999.0,
      "text": "In 1998, human embryonic stem cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226999.0,
      "end_time": 230511.0,
      "text": "were first identified, and just nine years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230511.0,
      "end_time": 234816.0,
      "text": "a group of scientists in Japan were able to take skin cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 234816.0,
      "end_time": 238110.0,
      "text": "and reprogram them with very powerful viruses"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 238110.0,
      "end_time": 242253.0,
      "text": "to create a kind of pluripotent stem cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 242253.0,
      "end_time": 244343.0,
      "text": "called an induced pluripotent stem cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 244343.0,
      "end_time": 247351.0,
      "text": "or what we refer to as an IPS cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 247351.0,
      "end_time": 250549.0,
      "text": "This was really an extraordinary advance, because"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 250549.0,
      "end_time": 253930.0,
      "text": "although these cells are not human embryonic stem cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253930.0,
      "end_time": 254887.0,
      "text": "which still remain the gold standard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 254887.0,
      "end_time": 258357.0,
      "text": "they are terrific to use for modeling disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 258357.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261870.00000000003,
      "text": "and potentially for drug discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 261870.0,
      "end_time": 264127.0,
      "text": "So a few months later, in 2008, one of our scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 264127.0,
      "end_time": 267327.0,
      "text": "built on that research. He took skin biopsies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267327.0,
      "end_time": 269355.0,
      "text": "this time from people who had a disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 269355.0,
      "end_time": 272269.0,
      "text": "ALS, or as you call it in the U.K., motor neuron disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 272269.0,
      "end_time": 273967.0,
      "text": "He turned them into the IPS cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 273967.0,
      "end_time": 276652.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve just told you about, and then he turned those"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 276653.0,
      "end_time": 279357.0,
      "text": "IPS cells into the motor neurons that actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 279357.0,
      "end_time": 280818.0,
      "text": "were dying in the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 280818.0,
      "end_time": 283837.0,
      "text": "So basically what he did was to take a healthy cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 283837.0,
      "end_time": 285551.0,
      "text": "and turn it into a sick cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285551.0,
      "end_time": 289109.0,
      "text": "and he recapitulated the disease over and over again"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 289109.0,
      "end_time": 292469.0,
      "text": "in the dish, and this was extraordinary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 292469.0,
      "end_time": 294717.0,
      "text": "because it was the first time that we had a model"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 294717.0,
      "end_time": 298905.0,
      "text": "of a disease from a living patient in living human cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 298905.0,
      "end_time": 302250.0,
      "text": "And as he watched the disease unfold, he was able"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 302250.0,
      "end_time": 305360.0,
      "text": "to discover that actually the motor neurons were dying"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 305360.0,
      "end_time": 307163.0,
      "text": "in the disease in a different way than the field"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 307163.0,
      "end_time": 309657.0,
      "text": "had previously thought. There was another kind of cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 309657.0,
      "end_time": 311858.0,
      "text": "that actually was sending out a toxin"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 311858.0,
      "end_time": 314369.0,
      "text": "and contributing to the death of these motor neurons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 314369.0,
      "end_time": 315727.0,
      "text": "and you simply couldn&#39;t see it"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 315727.0,
      "end_time": 317517.0,
      "text": "until you had the human model."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 317517.0,
      "end_time": 320183.0,
      "text": "So you could really say that"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 320184.0,
      "end_time": 324900.0,
      "text": "researchers trying to understand the cause of disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 324900.0,
      "end_time": 328241.0,
      "text": "without being able to have human stem cell models"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 328242.0,
      "end_time": 331200.0,
      "text": "were much like investigators trying to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 331200.0,
      "end_time": 334243.0,
      "text": "what had gone terribly wrong in a plane crash"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 334243.0,
      "end_time": 338240.0,
      "text": "without having a black box, or a flight recorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338240.0,
      "end_time": 340842.0,
      "text": "They could hypothesize about what had gone wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 340842.0,
      "end_time": 343954.0,
      "text": "but they really had no way of knowing what led"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 343954.0,
      "end_time": 346126.0,
      "text": "to the terrible events."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 346126.0,
      "end_time": 350308.0,
      "text": "And stem cells really have given us the black box"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 350309.0,
      "end_time": 354277.0,
      "text": "for diseases, and it&#39;s an unprecedented window."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 354277.0,
      "end_time": 357522.0,
      "text": "It really is extraordinary, because you can recapitulate"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 357522.0,
      "end_time": 360769.0,
      "text": "many, many diseases in a dish, you can see"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 360769.0,
      "end_time": 364305.0,
      "text": "what begins to go wrong in the cellular conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 364305.0,
      "end_time": 366729.0,
      "text": "well before you would ever see"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 366729.0,
      "end_time": 369265.0,
      "text": "symptoms appear in a patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 369265.0,
      "end_time": 371788.0,
      "text": "And this opens up the ability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 371788.0,
      "end_time": 374602.0,
      "text": "which hopefully will become something that"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 374602.0,
      "end_time": 377248.0,
      "text": "is routine in the near term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377249.0,
      "end_time": 381395.0,
      "text": "of using human cells to test for drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 381395.0,
      "end_time": 386859.0,
      "text": "Right now, the way we test for drugs is pretty problematic."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 386859.0,
      "end_time": 390176.0,
      "text": "To bring a successful drug to market, it takes, on average,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 390177.0,
      "end_time": 392363.0,
      "text": "13 years — that&#39;s one drug —"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 392363.0,
      "end_time": 395751.0,
      "text": "with a sunk cost of 4 billion dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 395751.0,
      "end_time": 400618.0,
      "text": "and only one percent of the drugs that start down that road"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 400618.0,
      "end_time": 402866.0,
      "text": "are actually going to get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 402866.0,
      "end_time": 404991.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t imagine other businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 404991.0,
      "end_time": 406440.0,
      "text": "that you would think of going into"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 406440.0,
      "end_time": 408195.0,
      "text": "that have these kind of numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 408195.0,
      "end_time": 409997.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a terrible business model."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 409997.0,
      "end_time": 413986.0,
      "text": "But it is really a worse social model because of"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 413986.0,
      "end_time": 417313.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s involved and the cost to all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 417314.0,
      "end_time": 421660.0,
      "text": "So the way we develop drugs now"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 421660.0,
      "end_time": 424265.0,
      "text": "is by testing promising compounds on --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 424266.0,
      "end_time": 426146.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t have disease modeling with human cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 426146.0,
      "end_time": 429610.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;d been testing them on cells of mice"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 429610.0,
      "end_time": 433277.0,
      "text": "or other creatures or cells that we engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 433277.0,
      "end_time": 436337.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t have the characteristics of the diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 436338.0,
      "end_time": 438674.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re actually trying to cure."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 438674.0,
      "end_time": 441719.0,
      "text": "You know, we&#39;re not mice, and you can&#39;t go into"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 441720.0,
      "end_time": 444138.0,
      "text": "a living person with an illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 444138.0,
      "end_time": 447660.0,
      "text": "and just pull out a few brain cells or cardiac cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 447660.0,
      "end_time": 449354.0,
      "text": "and then start fooling around in a lab to test"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 449355.0,
      "end_time": 452916.0,
      "text": "for, you know, a promising drug."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 452916.0,
      "end_time": 456501.0,
      "text": "But what you can do with human stem cells, now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 456501.0,
      "end_time": 460837.0,
      "text": "is actually create avatars, and you can create the cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 460838.0,
      "end_time": 462805.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s the live motor neurons"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 462805.0,
      "end_time": 465815.0,
      "text": "or the beating cardiac cells or liver cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 465815.0,
      "end_time": 469924.0,
      "text": "or other kinds of cells, and you can test for drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 469924.0,
      "end_time": 473490.0,
      "text": "promising compounds, on the actual cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 473490.0,
      "end_time": 476679.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re trying to affect, and this is now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 476680.0,
      "end_time": 479494.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s absolutely extraordinary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 479494.0,
      "end_time": 482650.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re going to know at the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 482650.0,
      "end_time": 486394.0,
      "text": "the very early stages of doing your assay development"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 486394.0,
      "end_time": 489783.0,
      "text": "and your testing, you&#39;re not going to have to wait 13 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 489783.0,
      "end_time": 493102.0,
      "text": "until you&#39;ve brought a drug to market, only to find out"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 493102.0,
      "end_time": 498157.0,
      "text": "that actually it doesn&#39;t work, or even worse, harms people."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 498158.0,
      "end_time": 502498.0,
      "text": "But it isn&#39;t really enough just to look at"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 502498.0,
      "end_time": 506280.0,
      "text": "the cells from a few people or a small group of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 506280.0,
      "end_time": 507924.0,
      "text": "because we have to step back."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 507924.0,
      "end_time": 509775.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got to look at the big picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 509775.0,
      "end_time": 512910.0,
      "text": "Look around this room. We are all different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 512909.99999999994,
      "end_time": 515649.99999999994,
      "text": "and a disease that I might have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 515650.0,
      "end_time": 518527.0,
      "text": "if I had Alzheimer&#39;s disease or Parkinson&#39;s disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 518528.0,
      "end_time": 522294.0,
      "text": "it probably would affect me differently than if"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 522294.0,
      "end_time": 523934.0,
      "text": "one of you had that disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 523933.99999999994,
      "end_time": 528280.0,
      "text": "and if we both had Parkinson&#39;s disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 528280.0,
      "end_time": 530548.0,
      "text": "and we took the same medication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 530548.0,
      "end_time": 533295.0,
      "text": "but we had different genetic makeup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 533295.0,
      "end_time": 535579.0,
      "text": "we probably would have a different result,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 535580.0,
      "end_time": 539311.0,
      "text": "and it could well be that a drug that worked wonderfully"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 539311.0,
      "end_time": 542890.0,
      "text": "for me was actually ineffective for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 542890.0,
      "end_time": 547582.0,
      "text": "and similarly, it could be that a drug that is harmful for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 547582.0,
      "end_time": 551884.0,
      "text": "is safe for me, and, you know, this seems totally obvious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 551884.0,
      "end_time": 554612.0,
      "text": "but unfortunately it is not the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 554612.0,
      "end_time": 557798.0,
      "text": "that the pharmaceutical industry has been developing drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 557798.0,
      "end_time": 561784.0,
      "text": "because, until now, it hasn&#39;t had the tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 561784.0,
      "end_time": 564760.0,
      "text": "And so we need to move away"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 564760.0,
      "end_time": 567300.0,
      "text": "from this one-size-fits-all model."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 567300.0,
      "end_time": 570207.0,
      "text": "The way we&#39;ve been developing drugs is essentially"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 570207.0,
      "end_time": 571586.0,
      "text": "like going into a shoe store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 571586.0,
      "end_time": 573869.0,
      "text": "no one asks you what size you are, or"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 573869.0,
      "end_time": 576790.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re going dancing or hiking."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 576790.0,
      "end_time": 578887.0,
      "text": "They just say, \"Well, you have feet, here are your shoes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 578887.0,
      "end_time": 582487.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t work with shoes, and our bodies are"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 582487.0,
      "end_time": 585959.0,
      "text": "many times more complicated than just our feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 585959.0,
      "end_time": 588500.0,
      "text": "So we really have to change this."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 588500.0,
      "end_time": 593684.0,
      "text": "There was a very sad example of this in the last decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 593684.0,
      "end_time": 596332.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a wonderful drug, and a class of drugs actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 596332.0,
      "end_time": 599120.0,
      "text": "but the particular drug was Vioxx, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 599120.0,
      "end_time": 603387.0,
      "text": "for people who were suffering from severe arthritis pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 603388.0,
      "end_time": 606780.0,
      "text": "the drug was an absolute lifesaver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 606780.0,
      "end_time": 611860.0,
      "text": "but unfortunately, for another subset of those people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 611860.0,
      "end_time": 616629.0,
      "text": "they suffered pretty severe heart side effects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 616629.0,
      "end_time": 619357.0,
      "text": "and for a subset of those people, the side effects were"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 619357.0,
      "end_time": 623254.0,
      "text": "so severe, the cardiac side effects, that they were fatal."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 623254.0,
      "end_time": 627296.0,
      "text": "But imagine a different scenario,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 627296.0,
      "end_time": 631598.0,
      "text": "where we could have had an array, a genetically diverse array,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 631598.0,
      "end_time": 635223.0,
      "text": "of cardiac cells, and we could have actually tested"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 635224.0,
      "end_time": 640305.0,
      "text": "that drug, Vioxx, in petri dishes, and figured out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 640305.0,
      "end_time": 644490.0,
      "text": "well, okay, people with this genetic type are going to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 644490.0,
      "end_time": 649490.0,
      "text": "cardiac side effects, people with these genetic subgroups"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 649490.0,
      "end_time": 654193.0,
      "text": "or genetic shoes sizes, about 25,000 of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 654193.0,
      "end_time": 656953.0,
      "text": "are not going to have any problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 656953.0,
      "end_time": 659568.0,
      "text": "The people for whom it was a lifesaver"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 659568.0,
      "end_time": 661245.0,
      "text": "could have still taken their medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 661245.0,
      "end_time": 665631.0,
      "text": "The people for whom it was a disaster, or fatal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 665631.0,
      "end_time": 667722.0,
      "text": "would never have been given it, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 667722.0,
      "end_time": 670305.0,
      "text": "you can imagine a very different outcome for the company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 670305.0,
      "end_time": 673730.0,
      "text": "who had to withdraw the drug."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 673730.0,
      "end_time": 675889.0,
      "text": "So that is terrific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 675889.0,
      "end_time": 677723.0,
      "text": "and we thought, all right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 677723.0,
      "end_time": 680482.0,
      "text": "as we&#39;re trying to solve this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 680482.0,
      "end_time": 682679.0,
      "text": "clearly we have to think about genetics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 682679.0,
      "end_time": 685512.0,
      "text": "we have to think about human testing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 685513.0,
      "end_time": 687920.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s a fundamental problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 687920.0,
      "end_time": 689790.0,
      "text": "because right now, stem cell lines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 689791.0,
      "end_time": 691501.0,
      "text": "as extraordinary as they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 691501.0,
      "end_time": 693245.0,
      "text": "and lines are just groups of cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 693245.0,
      "end_time": 697577.0,
      "text": "they are made by hand, one at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 697577.0,
      "end_time": 699801.0,
      "text": "and it takes a couple of months."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 699801.0,
      "end_time": 704167.0,
      "text": "This is not scalable, and also when you do things by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 704167.0,
      "end_time": 705710.0,
      "text": "even in the best laboratories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 705710.0,
      "end_time": 708871.0,
      "text": "you have variations in techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 708871.0,
      "end_time": 712520.0,
      "text": "and you need to know, if you&#39;re making a drug,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 712520.0,
      "end_time": 713950.0,
      "text": "that the Aspirin you&#39;re going to take out of the bottle"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 713950.0,
      "end_time": 716390.0,
      "text": "on Monday is the same as the Aspirin"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 716390.0,
      "end_time": 718471.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s going to come out of the bottle on Wednesday."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 718471.0,
      "end_time": 722262.0,
      "text": "So we looked at this, and we thought, okay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 722262.0,
      "end_time": 725414.0,
      "text": "artisanal is wonderful in, you know, your clothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 725414.0,
      "end_time": 728358.0,
      "text": "and your bread and crafts, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 728358.0,
      "end_time": 731340.0,
      "text": "artisanal really isn&#39;t going to work in stem cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 731341.0,
      "end_time": 733731.0,
      "text": "so we have to deal with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 733731.0,
      "end_time": 737651.0,
      "text": "But even with that, there still was another big hurdle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 737651.0,
      "end_time": 741214.0,
      "text": "and that actually brings us back to"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 741215.0,
      "end_time": 743599.0,
      "text": "the mapping of the human genome, because"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 743599.0,
      "end_time": 746310.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re all different."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 746310.0,
      "end_time": 749141.0,
      "text": "We know from the sequencing of the human genome"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 749142.0,
      "end_time": 751699.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s shown us all of the A&#39;s, C&#39;s, G&#39;s and T&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 751699.0,
      "end_time": 754166.0,
      "text": "that make up our genetic code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 754167.0,
      "end_time": 758436.0,
      "text": "but that code, by itself, our DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 758436.0,
      "end_time": 763350.0,
      "text": "is like looking at the ones and zeroes of the computer code"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 763350.0,
      "end_time": 765860.0,
      "text": "without having a computer that can read it."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 765860.0,
      "end_time": 769148.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like having an app without having a smartphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 769148.0,
      "end_time": 773320.0,
      "text": "We needed to have a way of bringing the biology"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 773320.0,
      "end_time": 775241.0,
      "text": "to that incredible data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 775241.0,
      "end_time": 778356.0,
      "text": "and the way to do that was to find"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 778356.0,
      "end_time": 781430.0,
      "text": "a stand-in, a biological stand-in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 781430.0,
      "end_time": 785680.0,
      "text": "that could contain all of the genetic information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 785680.0,
      "end_time": 787596.0,
      "text": "but have it be arrayed in such a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 787596.0,
      "end_time": 790460.0,
      "text": "as it could be read together"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 790460.0,
      "end_time": 793716.0,
      "text": "and actually create this incredible avatar."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 793716.0,
      "end_time": 797420.0,
      "text": "We need to have stem cells from all the genetic sub-types"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 797420.0,
      "end_time": 800372.0,
      "text": "that represent who we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 800372.0,
      "end_time": 803132.0,
      "text": "So this is what we&#39;ve built."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 803132.0,
      "end_time": 806452.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an automated robotic technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 806452.0,
      "end_time": 809600.0,
      "text": "It has the capacity to produce thousands and thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 809600.0,
      "end_time": 813299.0,
      "text": "of stem cell lines. It&#39;s genetically arrayed."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 813299.0,
      "end_time": 817480.0,
      "text": "It has massively parallel processing capability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 817480.0,
      "end_time": 820368.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going to change the way drugs are discovered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 820368.0,
      "end_time": 824203.0,
      "text": "we hope, and I think eventually what&#39;s going to happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 824203.0,
      "end_time": 826401.0,
      "text": "is that we&#39;re going to want to re-screen drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 826402.0,
      "end_time": 828893.0,
      "text": "on arrays like this, that already exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 828893.0,
      "end_time": 830764.0,
      "text": "all of the drugs that currently exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 830764.0,
      "end_time": 833675.0,
      "text": "and in the future, you&#39;re going to be taking drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 833675.0,
      "end_time": 836546.0,
      "text": "and treatments that have been tested for side effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 836547.0,
      "end_time": 838850.0,
      "text": "on all of the relevant cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 838850.0,
      "end_time": 842300.0,
      "text": "on brain cells and heart cells and liver cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 842300.0,
      "end_time": 845332.0,
      "text": "It really has brought us to the threshold"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 845332.0,
      "end_time": 847546.0,
      "text": "of personalized medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 847546.0,
      "end_time": 851987.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s here now, and in our family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 851987.0,
      "end_time": 854925.0,
      "text": "my son has type 1 diabetes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 854925.0,
      "end_time": 857573.0,
      "text": "which is still an incurable disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 857573.0,
      "end_time": 861150.0,
      "text": "and I lost my parents to heart disease and cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 861150.0,
      "end_time": 864747.0,
      "text": "but I think that my story probably sounds familiar to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 864748.0,
      "end_time": 868978.0,
      "text": "because probably a version of it is your story."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 868978.0,
      "end_time": 872921.0,
      "text": "At some point in our lives, all of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 872922.0,
      "end_time": 875658.0,
      "text": "or people we care about, become patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 875658.0,
      "end_time": 878267.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why I think that stem cell research"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 878267.0,
      "end_time": 881650.0,
      "text": "is incredibly important for all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 881650.0,
      "end_time": 885318.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 885318.0,
      "end_time": 892425.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}